áIN LOVING MEMORY OF BART MOORE-GILBERT, 1952-2015
Beloved father, lovely husband, dear friend, fabulous writer
We miss you so much, but you live on in our hearts
Love always, your 'sniggle' family, Anna, Maddy and Luke xxx"đ
í[LEFT]
"Don't cry because it's over, smile because it happened"
In loving memory of a dear friend and colleague
Adrian Rundin
9th December 1970 - 7th January 2007

[CENTRE]
"To live in hearts we leave behind is not to die"
In loving memory of a dear friend and colleague
Sheila Neagle
13th October 1946 - 24th September 2008


[RIGHT]
"It matters not how long you live, but how well"
In loving memory of a dear friend and colleague
Jay Taber
15th May 1978 - 25th February 2007"ň
